name: Jedi-autokey
tagline: My program for automating keypresses and eventually mouseclicks
body:
### Features
Autokey contains a CSGO Bhop script as well as a custom option for your own settings, the program is not done yet and lacks some significant features such as shortcut assignment and a way to use it while focused on another program.
Feel free to critique/leave suggestions

###Enjoy
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
